Nothing About Us Without Us? A Comparison of Adolescent and Adult Health-State 
Values for the Child Health Utility-9D Using Profile Case Best-Worst Scaling.

Ratcliffe J(1), Huynh E(2), Stevens K(3), Brazier J(3), Sawyer M(4), Flynn T(5).

Author information:
(1)Flinders Health Economics Group, Flinders University, Australia.
